author: Reuters Editorial
title: Web.Com Reports Q1 EPS $0.09
text:
May 3 (Reuters) - Web.com Group Inc:
* WEB.COM REPORTS FIRST QUARTER 2018 FINANCIAL RESULTS * Q1 REVENUE $187.8 MILLION VERSUS I/B/E/S VIEW $185.5 MILLION
* Q1 GAAP EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.09 * Q1 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $0.61 — THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* WEB.COM’S TOTAL NET SUBSCRIBERS WERE ABOUT 3,349,000 AT END OF Q1, DOWN ABOUT 62,000 FROM END OF Q4 OF 2017
* WEB.COM’S AVERAGE REVENUE PER USER WAS $18.34 IN Q1 COMPARED TO $17.67 FOR Q1 OF 2017 Source text for Eikon:
